Confluence permissions

Overview

In this tutorial we will discuss why it is important to know how to change permisions in confluence and learning why it is a good idea.

Why should we change permissions?

Changing permissions in confluence is important when it comes to guidlines in your company. You likely don't want a back-end developer making tasks for front-end developers, because thats not their jobs.
being able to change permissions allows for you to make sure the right people have the correct controls. Not only this but it allows for people to have their scopes set on the correct goals by only letting them view specific pages.


